These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, february, october, november, june
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, ebony, green, azure, yellow
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the person who likes ebony is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
 7. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is not the person who likes green##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
10. the person who likes lavender is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
11. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
13. the person who likes azure is not to the left of the person who likes green##8
14. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who likes green##7
15. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5     |
| Birthday        | february | october | june | november     | march    |
| Color   | green | yellow       | lavender   | azure | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, chaman, fonseca, bongani, cain
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, drawing, cooking, photography, traveling
 1. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 3. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
 5. the cain-smoker is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the bolivar-smoker##6
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bolivar-smoker##5
10. the cain-smoker is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
11. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Cigar   | bongani | cain    | bolivar | chaman  | fonseca |
| Hobby   | camping  | photography | traveling      | drawing | cooking |

