.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-3::.
House: modern, art-deco, ranch-style, colonial, farmhouse
There are 5 different favourite colors: orange, blue, amber, light-blue, grey
1. the modern house is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
2. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
3. the art-deco house is between the person who likes light-blue and the colonial house##2
4. the art-deco house is the person who likes amber##1
5. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
6. the modern house is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
7. the modern house is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |       3        |     4     |     5     |
| House           | colonial | art-deco | farmhouse | modern | ranch-style  |
| Color   | blue  | amber        | light-blue          | grey     | orange |

