.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-4::.
City: rome, edinburgh, berlin, san-francisco, liverpool
House: townhouse, ranch-style, tower, cottage, farmhouse
 1. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person traveling to edinburgh and the townhouse house##7
 2. the tower house is in an odd position##4
 3. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
 4. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
 5. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 6. the ranch-style house is not the person traveling to berlin##6
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 9. the ranch-style house is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to rome##7
10. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
12. the ranch-style house is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
13. the cottage house is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
14. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| City   | berlin | liverpool | san-francisco | rome | edinburgh |
| House           | townhouse    | ranch-style | farmhouse    | cottage      | tower      |

