.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-5::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, tram, boat, car, quad-bike
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks, video-games, skydiving, collecting
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 2. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 8. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 9. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
10. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |    3    |   4   |    5    |
| Transport      | tram   | train  | boat    | quad-bike | car |
| Hobby   | drawing | collecting | skydiving | magic-tricks | video-games   |

