.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-6::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, azalea, dahlia, daffodil, poppy
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, ivory, yellow, turquise, red
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 3. the person who likes apricot is not to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##8
 4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who growsbegonia##7
 6. the person who growspoppy is somewhere between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsdaffodil##7
 7. the person who likes red is the person who likes red##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growspoppy##2
 9. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the person who likes red##8
10. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
11. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
12. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Flower    | dahlia | daffodil | poppy     | begonia | azalea |
| Color   | yellow    | red    | ivory | apricot         | turquise   |

