.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-7::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, fantasy, superhero, action, sports
House: ranch-style, wooden, gothic-revival, tower, modern
 1. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
 2. the tower house is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
 3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the wooden house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the tower house##7
 5. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 6. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 7. the tower house is not the person watching mystery movies##6
 8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 9. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8
10. the tower house is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
11. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
12. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
13. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |   3    |   4    |     5     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | fantasy | action | sports | mystery |
| House           | modern     | ranch-style       | wooden | tower   | gothic-revival      |

