.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-8::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, handball, weightlifting, rugby, snowboarding
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch, indian, american, polish
 1. the dutch is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 2. the american is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the dutch##8
 4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the indian##8
 6. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the indian and the egyptian##7
10. the indian is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the egyptian##6
12. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |  4   |    5    |
| Sport   | rugby    | volleyball      | snowboarding | handball | weightlifting |
| Nationality     | indian | dutch | american    | egyptian  | polish  |

