.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-9::.
There 5 different types of food: strawberry, grapes, asparagus, broccoli, pepper
City: rome, san-francisco, berlin, marseilles, liverpool
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
 7. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
 8. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 9. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
10. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4     |      5      |
| Food           | pepper | strawberry | broccoli | grapes   | asparagus |
| City   | san-francisco     | liverpool  | marseilles     | berlin | rome   |

