 5. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 6. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating lemon is in an odd position##4
 8. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person eating broccoli##5
 9. the fan of rock is not the person eating radish##6
10. the fan of ambient is not to the left of the person eating radish##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |     5     |
