 4. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching satire movies##7
 5. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
 6. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
 7. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
